<h3>What is SMSBump?</h3>
<p><a href="http://smsbump.com/" target="_blank	">SMSBump</a> is a cloud-based reliable interface for sending SMS, Voice (VMS), MMS and USSD messages to 200+ networks around the world.</p>
<h3>How to create an API key?</h3>
<p>If you want to use the plugin for SMSBump, you need to create an API key. You can do this by signing up <a href="http://smsbump.com/users/signup"><strong>here</strong></a>.  The account creation is free and gives you credit to start.</p>
